      "line": 66,
      "message": "Suggestion for general architecture - please ignore if this is a master plan and this MR is only a part of it.\n\nIMHO we should return an instance of AaiHttpClient initialized with this HttpClient. AaiHttpClient should be a base interface for all AAI requests (ie. AaiHttpGetClient and AaiHttpPatchClient). It should contain single method (apply/invoke/...).\n\nHere instead of build() we should have get() and patch() methods.",
